; Gloaming's three hand-authored phrases, transcribed from
; code-samples/sinclair-zx-spectrum/assembly/gloaming/prototype/gloaming.asm.
; The calibration fixture: regenerating these must reproduce the prototype's
; constants exactly (decisions/demand-gate-beeper-phrases.md § Fidelity rule).

phrase chime_dusk          ; the title — two bell notes, high then low
  E5  299ms                ; a bright strike
  rest 8
  C5  398ms                ; C5 answers, a shade longer

phrase fanfare_held        ; THE NIGHT IS HELD — a rising run
  C5  250ms
  rest 3
  E5  250ms
  rest 3
  G5  250ms
  rest 3
  C6  487ms                ; held on the top

phrase sting_nightfall     ; NIGHT FALLS — two steps down, then dark
  E5  125ms
  rest 4
  D5  124ms
  rest 4
  A4  500ms                ; A4, long — the night settles on it
